ISLAMABAD, Jul 10 (APP): Minister for Information and Broadcasting Marriyum Aurangzeb late on Saturday greeted all the Muslims including Pakistani citizens and expats on the occasion of Eid-ul-Azha.
“Sacrifice means compassion, altruism, obedience, tolerance and humanity, which is liked by the Almighty Allah,” the minister tweeted while saying “Eid Mubarak” to all.
